text: The 1989–90 season ended for First Vienna FC with an eighth-place finish in the domestic league. During this season the club played for their second time in a European competition when they have been eliminated in the second round of the 1989–90 UEFA Cup. ==Squad== ===Squad and statistics=== |- ! colspan="12" style="background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center;"| Goalkeepers |- ! colspan="12" style="background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center;"| Defenders |- ! colspan="12" style="background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center;"| Midfielders |- ! colspan="12" style="background:#dcdcdc; text-align:center;"| Forwards |} ==References== Category:First Vienna FC
